'''亞曼德·道格拉斯·「艾米」·漢默'''（{{lang-en|Armand Douglas "Armie" Hammer}}，{{bd|1986年|8月28日}}）<ref name=yahoo>{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/person/armie-hammer/biography.html|title=Armie Hammer biography|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo! Movies]]|accessdate=2013-04-25|archive-date=2014-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225020943/https://movies.yahoo.com/person/armie-hammer/biography.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一名[[美國|美國]][[男演員|男演員]]，知名作品如電影《[[社群網戰|社群網戰]]》（2010年）<ref name="ReferenceA">[http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-social-network "The Social Network reviews, ratings, credits, and more at Metacritic"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-social-network |date=20100819061951 }}, ''Metacritic'', October 2010</ref>、《[[強·艾德格|強·艾德格]]》（2011年）和《[[特務型戰|特務型戰]]》（2015年）。

==早期生活==
漢默出生於美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]洛杉磯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nymag.com/movies/features/armie-hammer-2011-11/|title=J. Edgar Hoover’s Trophy Boy|publisher=New York Magazine|date=2011-11-07|accessdate=2018-04-23|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213120854/https://nymag.com/movies/features/armie-hammer-2011-11/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漢默把自己描述為「半猶太人（half Jewish）」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wmagazine.com/gallery/hollywood-leading-men-ss/all|title=Jim Sturgess: Seriously Sexy|publisher=W Magazine|accessdate=2010-09-01|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327101118/https://www.wmagazine.com/gallery/hollywood-leading-men-ss/all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。母親德魯·安（Dru Ann）的娘家姓為莫布里（Mobley），是一名前銀行信貸員<ref name=eht>{{Cite news|title=Miss Mobley Has Nuptials In Oklahoma|publisher=The New York Times|date=1985-01-13|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1985/01/13/style/miss-mobley-has-nuptials-in-oklahoma.html|accessdate=2010-10-05|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116190545/https://www.nytimes.com/1985/01/13/style/miss-mobley-has-nuptials-in-oklahoma.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親{{link-en|麥可·亞曼德·漢默|Michael Armand Hammer}}是擁有多項生意的慈善家與商人<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Smith|title='Network' twin has ties with Tulsa: Armie Hammer connects to Mobleys, Hammers|date=2010-10-22|url=http://www.tulsaworld.com/scene/article.aspx?subjectid=268&articleid=20101022_283_D1_CUTLIN603839|work=[[Tulsa_World|Tulsa World]]|accessdate=2010-10-22|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012112332/http://www.tulsaworld.com/scene/article.aspx?subjectid=268&articleid=20101022_283_D1_CUTLIN603839|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joycemeyer.org/AboutUs/DruHammerBio.aspx|title=Dru Hammer – Board Member|publisher=joycemeyer.org|accessdate=2012-01-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201201147/http://www.joycemeyer.org/AboutUs/DruHammerBio.aspx|archivedate=2016-12-01}}</ref>。他有一個名為維克托（Viktor）的弟弟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/armie-hammer/bio/332606|title=Armie Hammer|publisher=TV Guide|accessdate=2015-05-05|archive-date=2014-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606204232/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/armie-hammer/bio/332606|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

漢默的曾祖父[[亞曼德·漢默|亞曼德·漢默]]是石油大亨兼慈善家，是[[俄羅斯猶太人|俄羅斯猶太人]]後裔<ref>{{cite web|first=Caroline|last=Redmond|url=http://people.com/movies/5-things-you-probably-dont-know-about-armie-hammer/|title=5 Things You Probably Don't Know About Armie Hammer|publisher=People Magazine|date=2017-11-21|accessdate=2018-04-23|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113102641/https://people.com/movies/5-things-you-probably-dont-know-about-armie-hammer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Seth|last=Abramovitch|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/features/armie-hammer-his-steamy-new-movie-a-charmed-upbringing-oscars-double-standards-1059752|title=Armie Hammer on His Steamy New Movie, a Charmed Upbringing and Oscar's "Double Standards"|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2017-11-20|accessdate=2018-04-23|archive-date=2017-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171120181517/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/features/armie-hammer-his-steamy-new-movie-a-charmed-upbringing-oscars-double-standards-1059752|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-4968669.html|title=Hammer|publisher=HighBeam Research|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202040554/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-4968669.html|archive-date=2017-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[亞曼德·漢默|亞曼德·漢默]]的父母Julius Hammer和Rose是從俄國移居到美國的[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jta.org/1990/12/12/archive/armand-hammer-dead-at-92-on-eve-of-his-bar-mitzvah|title=Armand Hammer Dead at 92 on Eve of His Bar Mitzvah|publisher=JTA - Jewish news|accessdate=2017-11-20|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327085806/https://www.jta.org/1990/12/12/archive/armand-hammer-dead-at-92-on-eve-of-his-bar-mitzvah|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
2007年，漢默受[[喬治·米勒|喬治·米勒]]經過漫長的尋找後點名在[[正義聯盟|正義聯盟]]電影《Justice League: Mortal》中飾演[[蝙蝠俠|布魯斯·韋恩／蝙蝠俠]]。該電影將由米勒執導，但後來因米勒退出而取消<ref name="eo1">{{cite news|work=[[E!_Online|E! Online]]|title=Holy Double Take, Batman! Here Comes a New Caped Crusader|url=http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/marc_malkin/b30975_holy_double_take_batman_here_comes_new.html|date=2008-09-25|first=Marc|last=Malkin|accessdate=2015-06-01|archive-date=2008-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081104103251/http://www.eonline.com/uberblog/marc_malkin/b30975_holy_double_take_batman_here_comes_new.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

漢默於2013年上映的電視劇改編電影《[[獨行俠_(2013年電影)|獨行俠]]》中與[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]共同主演<ref>{{cite web|author=24 Like15 Dislike0 May 17, 2011 by B. Alan Orange|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/armie-hammer-is-the-lone-ranger|title=Armie Hammer Is the Lone Ranger!|publisher=MovieWeb.com|date=2011-05-17|accessdate=2012-01-26|archive-date=2013-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208001554/http://www.movieweb.com/news/armie-hammer-is-the-lone-ranger|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Jordan|first=Richard|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/cannes-2011-armie-hammer-signs-on-for-2-22|title=Cannes 2011: Armie Hammer signs on for 2:22|publisher=TotalFilm.com|date=2011-05-14|accessdate=2012-01-26|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202222203/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/cannes-2011-armie-hammer-signs-on-for-2-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，宣布他將演出[[蓋·瑞奇|蓋·瑞奇]]執導的1960年代電視劇改編電影《[[紳士密令|紳士密令]]》，與[[亨利·卡維爾|亨利·卡維爾]]共同主演，並於2015年上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/lone-ranger-armie-hammer-to-star-with-tom-cruise-in-man-from-u-n-c-l-e|title=‘Lone Ranger’ Armie Hammer To Star With Tom Cruise In ‘Man From U.N.C.L.E.’|first=Mike Jr.|last=Fleming|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2013-04-24|accessdate=2013-04-25|archive-date=2014-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214004953/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/lone-ranger-armie-hammer-to-star-with-tom-cruise-in-man-from-u-n-c-l-e/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://usatoday.com/article/news/2384785 'Man of Steel' star Henry Cavill needs nerves of steel]{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, usatoday.com; accessed February 16, 2015.</ref>。漢默還於2016年電影《[[國家的誕生|國家的誕生]]》中飾演山繆·透納一角。

2016年5月，漢默確認演出《[[请以你的名字呼唤我_(电影)|以你的名字呼喚我]]》，並與[[堤摩西·柴勒梅德|堤摩西·柴勒梅德]]和[[麥可·斯圖巴|麥可·斯圖巴]]共同主演。該片改編自{{link-en|安德烈·阿基曼|André Aciman}}的[[以你的名字呼喚我_(小說)|同名小說]]，由[[盧卡·格達戈尼諾|盧卡·格達戈尼諾]]執導，並於2016年5月開始拍攝，於2017年在聖丹斯首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thefilmstage.com/news/michael-stuhlbarg-armie-hammer-more-leading-luca-guadagninos-call-me-by-your-name/|title=Michael Stuhlbarg, Armie Hammer & More Leading Luca Guadagnino’s ‘Call Me By Your Name’|publisher=The Film Stage|date=2016-05-23|accessdate=2016-05-24|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624025911/https://thefilmstage.com/news/michael-stuhlbarg-armie-hammer-more-leading-luca-guadagninos-call-me-by-your-name/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
在2008年的一次訪談中，漢默透露對自己宗教信仰的想法，「我有自己的精神生活，我非常地重視」<ref>[http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2008/octoberweb-only/armiehammer.html?start=1 Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2008/octoberweb-only/armiehammer.html?start=1 |date=20200812180258 }}, christianitytoday.com; accessed February 16, 2015.</ref>。

2010年，漢默與電視名人伊麗莎白·錢伯斯（Elizabeth Chambers）結婚，並在教堂舉行婚禮<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSOtLm3Oclc |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-12-23 |archive-date=2017-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408010603/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSOtLm3Oclc |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這由漢默的藝術家朋友{{link-en|泰勒·拉姆齊|Tyler Ramsey}}介紹認識<ref>{{Cite news|title=Zac Efron's Star Studded Saturday|publisher=The Insider|date=2011-11-07|url=http://www.theinsider.com/gossip/45973_Mikey_Glazer_Celeb_Sightings_November_7/index.html|accessdate=2015-06-01|archive-date=2011-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111108135857/http://www.theinsider.com/gossip/45973_Mikey_Glazer_Celeb_Sightings_November_7/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年10月1日，兩人有了一個名為哈波（Harper）的女嬰<ref>{{cite web|author1=Bruna Nessif|title=Armie Hammer and Wife Elizabeth Chambers Hammer Welcome a Baby Girl!|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/599719/armie-hammer-and-wife-elizabeth-chambers-hammer-welcome-a-baby-girl|publisher=[[E!|E!]]|accessdate=2015-03-31|date=2014-12-02|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205041634/https://www.eonline.com/news/599719/armie-hammer-and-wife-elizabeth-chambers-hammer-welcome-a-baby-girl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
2017年1月15日，他们的第二个儿子出生，取名Ford Armand Douglas Hammer<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://people.com/babies/armie-hammer-elizabeth-chambers-welcome-son-ford-douglas-armand/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-09-19 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019063748/http://people.com/babies/armie-hammer-elizabeth-chambers-welcome-son-ford-douglas-armand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
2020年7月與與妻子伊麗莎白·錢伯斯（Elizabeth Chambers）離婚。

